<item>
            <title>[SPR-2004] Update schema to allow custom XML configuration inside the constructor-arg tag</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2004</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Update schema to allow custom XML configuration inside constructor-arg tag&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ie, If i want to pass a custom component defined usign new custom XML i can&apos;t do this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  &amp;lt;constructor-arg&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;foo:bar /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/constructor-arg&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This just looks like a missing entry in shema; XmlBeanDefinitionParserHelper does handle this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
